headline: ONEOK Announces Completion of NGL Fractionation and Pipeline Expansion Projects
summary: ONEOK, Inc. (NYSE: OKE) today announced the completion of MB-6, a 125,000-barrel per day (bpd) natural gas liquids (NGL) fractionator in Mont Belvieu, Texas, and the full looping of the West Texas NGL Pipeline system.
